	"never" FLOAT,

	"sometimes" FLOAT,
	"frequently" FLOAT,
	"always" FLOAT
);

	"country" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"placename" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"frequency" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"start_date" DATE,
	"end_date" DATE,
	"year" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"month" NUMBER(38,0),
	"week" NUMBER(38,0),
	"deaths" NUMBER(38,0),
	"expected_deaths" NUMBER(38,0),
	"excess_deaths" NUMBER(38,0),
	"baseline" VARCHAR(16777216)
);

create or replace TABLE US_COUNTIES (
	"date" DATE,
	"county" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"state_name" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"county_fips_code" VARCHAR(16777216),
	"confirmed_cases" NUMBER(38,0),
	"deaths" NUMBER(38,0)
);

create or replace TABLE US_STATES (
	"date" DATE,
	"state_name" VARCHAR(16777216),

	"deaths" NUMBER(38,0)
